## G9 Specs Workspace with Bidirectional Traceability
**Status:** implemented
**Depends on:** G7, G8

Specs are not flat documents — they form a live decision pyramid. Every Plan traces back to a Goal, every Test verifies a Design. The frontend makes this traceability the primary navigation model.

